  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Visit someone in prison during the coronavirus (COVID-19) pandemic
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Prisons in England and Wales will now be opening when they decide it is safe for visitors. </p>

  </div>
</div>

